Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy outlines how 24 HIT Riga SIA collects and processes your personal data when you use our mobile applications (the "App").
The App is free to play with optional in-game purchases. To maintain high quality and a great gaming experience, we process information about you to improve the App and support internal operations.
We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. If changes are made, we will notify you by revising the date at the top of the policy and, depending on the changes, we may provide additional notice or require renewed consent.
Collection of Information
Information We Collect Automatically
When you access or use the App, we automatically collect general information, including:
Log Information
: Details about your use of the App, such as device type, features used, access times, and IP address.
Device Information
: Information about your device, including manufacturer, model, operating system, time zone, and language.
Device Identifiers
: Online identifiers of your device, such as IDFA, Google Ads ID, Google Device ID, Game Center ID, and Google Play Account ID.
Usage Information
: Information related to your use of the App, such as game progress, scores, achievements, and interactions with other players.
Consumption Information
: Details about your consumption habits within the App, including purchases made with virtual and real currencies and the reception of virtual goods in-game.
Information We Collect from Other Sources
If you log into the App using a third-party site or platform like Facebook, Apple Game Center, or Google Sign-In, we access information from that site or platform, such as your screen name, profile information, and friend lists, in accordance with their authorization procedures and your consent.
For more information about how these third parties process your data, refer to their privacy policies:
Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/about/privacy/
Game Center:
https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/gamecenter/
Google Play Games:
https://policies.google.com/privacy
Use of Information
We use your information for the following purposes, in accordance with the legal bases for each type of personal data as described below:
Log, Device, Usage, and Consumption Information and Device Identifiers
:
To provide and deliver requested products and services and send you related information.
To maintain the App and game experience.
To send technical notices, updates, security alerts, and support and administrative messages.
Our processing for these purposes is necessary for the performance of a contract to support the App, facilitate the delivery of products and services, and maintain and update the App (Article 6(1)(b) of the GDPR).
To Provide News and Information
:
To personalize and improve the App and provide tailored content and features.
To monitor and analyze trends, usage, and activities in connection with the App.
Our processing for these purposes is justified by our legitimate interests in providing content of interest and improving our services (Article 6(1)(f) of the GDPR).
To Provide Personalized Advertisements
:
For users who have given consent, to share their advertising IDs with ad network partners for personalized advertisements in the App (behavioral advertising).
This processing is justified by our legitimate interests (Article 6(1)(f) of the GDPR) and is based on your consent for sharing advertising IDs with third parties (Article 6(1)(a) of the GDPR).
Information from Other Sources
:
To provide and deliver requested products and services.
To link or combine information from others to better understand your needs and provide improved service.
To provide news and information about the App that we think will be of interest to you.
This processing is justified by our legitimate interests in providing content of interest and improving our services (Article 6(1)(f) of the GDPR).
We process your information only as necessary to achieve the purposes for which it was collected.
Storage of Information
24 HIT Riga SIA will store your personal data for as long as necessary to provide you with the App or fulfill the purposes described above unless further storage is required for legal reasons. Your data will be deleted or anonymized once it no longer serves these purposes, and in any case, no later than three years after your interaction with 24 HIT Riga SIA has ceased.
Sharing of Information
We disclose information about you to the following categories of recipients based on the legal bases under Sections 6(1)(b), 6(1)(c), and 6(1)(f) of the GDPR:
Social Networks
: As described under "Social Sharing Features."
Third Parties
: If required by law, regulation, legal process, or during negotiations of any merger, sale, or acquisition.
Authorities
: If necessary to protect the rights, property, and safety of 24 HIT Riga SIA or others.
Other Players
: To provide certain in-app features like leaderboards if you log in using a third-party service.
If you have given consent under Section 6(1)(a) of the GDPR, we share your device identifiers with advertising network companies for behavioral advertising in the App. We use or may use the following advertising network companies:
